{"tid":790402,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［jj插沙］有無巴打知道呢幾隻pc game？","createTime":"2018-08-23T03:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T04:14:33.000Z","uid":166637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf730fe5f6cd0dede31b2eaceb115b6f3fd88b4","tid":790402,"uid":166637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"最近想玩返細個d單機game<br />\n但google個名又搵唔到 有d個名又唔sure<br />\n<br />\n1. 瘋狂企鵝村<br />\n有好撚多關 玩法類似mario <br />\n畫面有隻細細既企鵝 要係指定時間過關<br />\n企鵝需要不停向前進 有寶箱要開<br />\n好似有成40幾 定多過40幾關<br />\n有一關係隻企鵝要食魚 之後就可以潛水去收集d野<br />\nsorry for1999 因爲太細個玩過 記性太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明記得叫瘋狂企鵝村<br />\n但上網search唔到<br />\n<br />\n2.蠟筆小新pc game<br />\n係冒險遊戲黎 成個畫面跟住移動<br />\n小新中途要打怪物 我記得好似打過松板老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有落過下水道<br />\n<br />\n3. 動物園/度假村 pc game<br />\n曾經search過模擬動物園/動物園大享<br />\n但都唔係我細個玩個隻黎<br />\n動物園我記得係先起左個動物區，再買動物放入去<br />\nd動物會生bb<br />\n最記得倉鼠/台灣叫土撥鼠、兔仔<br />\n<br />\n度假村又係search過模擬度假村<br />\n不過唔係我想玩個隻<br />\n有無人玩過度假村game但唔係叫模擬度假村？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢隻game特色比較少，我都唔太記得<br />\n記得可以起碼頭酒店咋<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送上大波台妹j圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfde7e6146e8c5602b62fd6e96b4fe236d2718e6","tid":790402,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"我都玩過模擬度假村，但係上網搵極都搵唔返細個玩過果隻。"},{"pid":"57112887e8bd2d589fe355531861144a63fb0e93","tid":790402,"uid":195030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:50